We provide services around
GraphSense
the leading open source Cryptoasset Analytics platform

Dashboard

The dashboard allows users to visualize and understand cryptoasset flows.

Programmatic access

Our solution is a fully-fledged data science platform tailored to cryptoasset analytics tasks. Customers can use our API for automated, highly efficient forensics tasks.

Supported assets

We support UTXO-model ledgers like Bitcoin, Bitcoin Cash, Litecoin, and Zcash as well as account-model blockchains like Ethereum.

Full data sovereignty

Our solution relies on full data sovereignty, algorithmic transparency, and scalability. It is hosted entirely in Europe, and with our partners, we are building a comprehensive attribution tag collection.
